hwpwm_chip_open_index(3)

# NAME

_hwpwm\_chip\_open\_index_ - Open PWM chip object at index

# SYNOPSIS

#include <hwpwm.h>

struct hwpwm\_chip \*_hwpwm\_chip\_open\_index_(unsigned i, int \*error);

# DESCRIPTION

Opens the _export_, _unexport_, _npwm_ files for the  PWM chip at
/sys/class/pwm/pwmchip_i_.

The *i* parameter is the index of the PWM chip.

If the function fails and *error* is not _NULL_, the integer it's pointing to
is set to the last error code.

# RETURN VALUES

This function returns a pointer to an opaque _struct hwpwm\_chip_ or _NULL_ if
it failed.

